&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harbor&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Contracts Lawyer&lt;/strong&gt; to join our growing consulting delivery team in the Philippines. By providing strategic, technology, and operational services to clients in the legal, professional, and financial services industries&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;O&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;ur Contracts Counsel&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Team&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;a highly talented&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;No Spacing&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;group of legal professionals who offer a unique blend of consulting and legal experience across several industries and disciplines.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
