&lt;p class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot; data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harbor&lt;/strong&gt; is seeking a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager, Research &amp;amp; Intelligence&lt;/strong&gt; to lead delivery of high-quality legal, business, and competitive intelligence services for our clients.&amp;nbsp;This role is responsible for overseeing research operations, managing team performance, and ensuring the delivery of accurate, timely, and actionable research outputs. The Senior Manager will also drive continuous improvement in research workflows, tools, and service delivery models, while supporting client engagements and internal strategic initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;This is a remote position. Candidates must be able to work effectively in a distributed, global team environment.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
