&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Manage and prioritize incoming research workflows, ensuring timely completion&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Ongoing optimization of research processes, including intake, triage, execution, and delivery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Monitor service performance and identify opportunities for efficiency and improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Oversee staffing, utilization, and workload allocation across research teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Lead, coach, and develop research and intelligence professionals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Support recruitment, onboarding, and training programs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Partner with internal teams to align research services with technology, tools, and knowledge systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;x_MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Contribute to the development of new services, capabilities, and client solutions&lt;/li&gt;
